name: OOZY•GOOZEMO (Runes)
description: Oozy Goozemo is a silly, smiling slug slowly making its way through the layers of the Karmic Grid. In it's wake an everpresent cosmic trail of mucus, a testament to the mark Oozy leaves in our souls and hearts. If you take the time to watch closely you will surely find Oozy in all its beauty on the Bitcoin blockchain. Yes, it may be slow, but you know how the saying goes: Slowly first, then all at once.
